snippet.title: GODZILLA (Commodore 16 & Commodore Plus/4) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay showcase of the extremely obscure [unlicensed] Hungarian Godzilla video game from 1988! As you may clearly see, this is absolutely in no way Godzilla... it's just a straight-up dinosaur. This game has literally no end, and you can't even get a high score. 

http://wikizilla.org/wiki/Godzilla_(Commodore_Plus/4%29

Facebook!
https://facebook.com/GodzillaWiki
And of course, visit Wikizilla!
